<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạis̊mu yasūʿa qad̊ samā
 waqad̊ ʿalạa wafāq̊
 biạl̊ʿāri wāl̊maẘti ạlãdẖī
 biạlnĩʿ̊maẗi qad̊ dẖāq̊

[V2]
 2- qadi ạs̊tahāna biạl̊kẖajal̊
 faʿan̊ yamīni ạllh̊
 biạl̊maj̊di qāma wān̊faṣal̊
 dẖāka ʿani ạl̊kẖuṭāh̊

[V3]
 3- yā ʿajabaⁿạ min̊ faḍ̊li man̊
 qāma bimaj̊di ạlậb̊
 baʿ̊da ạtĩḍāʿiⁿ ṭāyỉʿaⁿạ
 lil̊maẘti wāl̊ʿadẖāb̊

[V4]
 4- waṣāra ạảʿ̊lay̱ min̊
 samāwātiⁿ mukalãlạ
 waḍāminaⁿạ ʿah̊daⁿạ samā
 jidaⁿ̃ạ wāảf̊ḍalạ

[V5]
 5- kulũ ạlsũrūri wālrĩḍay̱
 bihi ạảmāma ạlậb̊
 waqal̊buhu bikulĩ mā
 ạảk̊malahu qad̊ ṭāb̊

[V6]
 6- fal̊yak̊tafi ạl̊qal̊bu biman̊
 bihi ạk̊tafay̱ ạl̊qadīr̊
 wal̊tab̊tahij̊ nufūsunā
 bimaj̊dihi ạl̊munīr̊</lyrics>
<title>ạsm yswʿ qd smạ</title>
